sec.p:
In order to model the whole system, multi-physics approach was adopted including the resource, the marine turbine, and the ESS. This simulator can evaluate marine current turbine performances and dynamic loads over different operating conditions. Throughout the paper, we will use P=(T0,TP)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
